 filch whats going on 
 
 filch stopped a few steps below harry and turned at the foot of the stairs stood the only person who could make situation worse snape he was wearing a long gray nightshirt and he looked livid 
 
 its peeves professor filch whispered malevolently he threw this egg down the stairs 
 
