 i yes professor but 
 
 filch looked yearningly up the stairs right through harry who could see that he was very reluctant to forgo the chance of cornering peeves go harry pleaded with him silently go with snapegomrs norris was peering around had the distinct impression that she could smell had he filled that bath with so much perfumed foam 
 
