 course dumbledore trusts you growled moody hes a trusting man he believes in second chances but me i say there are spots that come off snape spots that never come off know what i mean 
 
 snape suddenly did something very strange he seized his left forearm convulsively with his right hand as though something on it had hurt him 
 
 moody laughed get back to bed snape 
 
