 it is youth demanding pity of the old man of you are entering into life i am leaving it you go to the play to balls to the cafe to the you have wit you please the women you are a handsome fellow as for me i spit on my brands in the heart of summer you are rich with the only riches that are really such i possess all the poverty of age infirmity isolation 
